    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一-介词的含义"><a href="#一-介词的含义" class="headerlink" title="(一) 介词的含义"></a>(一) 介词的含义</h1><p>​    英语前置词（preposition ，adposition的一种，还有后置词postposition），表示名词、代词等与句中其它词的关系，在句中不能单独作<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%A5%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E5%88%86/5695962">句子成分</a>。介词后面一般有名词、代词或相当于名词的其他<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%AF%8D%E7%B1%BB/5310343">词类</a>、短语或从句作它的<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AE%BE%E8%AF%AD/87544">宾语</a>，表示与其他成分的关系。</p><p>前置词和它的宾语构成介词<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%AF%8D%E7%BB%84/8481390">词组</a>，在句中作<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%8A%B6%E8%AF%AD/882">状语</a>，<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%A1%A8%E8%AF%AD/2017501">表语</a>，<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%A1%A5%E8%AF%AD/2647235">补语</a>，<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AE%9A%E8%AF%AD/2645898">定语</a>或介词宾语。同时介词的用法也很灵活，同一个介词可以表达多种意义，介词可以分为<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%8B%E8%AF%8D/6697743">时间介词</a>、地点介词、方式介词、原因介词、数量介词和其他介词。</p><p>前置词一般用于<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D/502047">名词</a>或者代词前面，表示该词与句中其他成分的关系。前置词后面的名词或代词称为前置词的宾语（如果是<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%B0%E4%BB%A3%E8%AF%8D/10189208">人称代词</a>，则要用宾格）。前置和宾语合在一起构成前置词短语。</p><h1 id="二-介词的构成形式"><a href="#二-介词的构成形式" class="headerlink" title="(二) 介词的构成形式"></a>(二) 介词的构成形式</h1><h2 id="简单介词-prep"><a href="#简单介词-prep" class="headerlink" title="简单介词(prep)"></a>简单介词(prep)</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">in在...里; ...</span><br><span class="line">to朝; ...</span><br><span class="line">with...和; ...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="短语介词"><a href="#短语介词" class="headerlink" title="短语介词"></a>短语介词</h2><p>​    视作介词，不单独表完整意义</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">by way of通过...方式 &lt;=介词+名词+介词</span><br><span class="line">at the end of在...的最后&lt;=介词+the+名词</span><br><span class="line">along with和...在一起&lt;=介词+介词</span><br><span class="line">because of因为...&lt;=连词+介词</span><br><span class="line">previous to...之前&lt;=形容词+介词</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="合成介词"><a href="#合成介词" class="headerlink" title="合成介词"></a>合成介词</h2><p>​    <code>动词的分词充当</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">into (in-to)到...之内</span><br><span class="line">onto (on-to)到...之上</span><br><span class="line">within (with-in)在...之内</span><br><span class="line">notwithstanding(not with standing)尽管</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="分词介词"><a href="#分词介词" class="headerlink" title="分词介词"></a>分词介词</h2><p><code>一般用动词的分词形式表示</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">including包括...</span><br><span class="line">regarding关于...;至于...</span><br><span class="line">considering鉴于...;考虑到...</span><br><span class="line">given考虑到...;如果...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="三-介词的用法"><a href="#三-介词的用法" class="headerlink" title="(三)介词的用法"></a>(三)介词的用法</h1><h2 id="空间介词"><a href="#空间介词" class="headerlink" title="空间介词"></a>空间介词</h2><h3 id="in-在…里面"><a href="#in-在…里面" class="headerlink" title="in    在…里面"></a><strong>in    在…里面</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">in the house在房屋里</span><br><span class="line">in the park在公园里</span><br><span class="line">in the country在国内</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="on-在…上面"><a href="#on-在…上面" class="headerlink" title="on    在…上面"></a><strong>on    在…上面</strong></h3><p><code>与物体有接触表示在某个面上的含义</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">on the table在桌子上</span><br><span class="line">on the floor在地板上</span><br><span class="line">in thetree这里指(外部事物)在树的里面如:鸟,乌鸦等</span><br><span class="line">on the tree指长在树上的如:苹果,叶子等</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="at-在某处"><a href="#at-在某处" class="headerlink" title="at    在某处"></a><strong>at    在某处</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">at the corner of the street在街道拐角</span><br><span class="line">at the bus station在公交车车站</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="over-覆盖-在…上方-越过上方"><a href="#over-覆盖-在…上方-越过上方" class="headerlink" title="over    覆盖;在…上方;越过上方"></a><strong>over    覆盖;在…上方;越过上方</strong></h3><p><code>可与物体接触或不接触，一般特指正上方</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The mother put over a blanket over the child(覆盖) </span><br><span class="line">妈妈把毯子盖在孩子的身上</span><br><span class="line">the bridge over the river(在...上方)</span><br><span class="line">在河上的桥</span><br><span class="line">the lamp over the table(在...上方)</span><br><span class="line">在桌上方的灯</span><br><span class="line">the plane flew over the mountain(越过上方)</span><br><span class="line">飞机飞越过高山</span><br><span class="line">The cat climbed over the fence</span><br><span class="line">猫爬过栅栏</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="above-在…的上方"><a href="#above-在…的上方" class="headerlink" title="above    在…的上方"></a>above    在…的上方</h3><p><code>一般指物体上方高出这个平面就行</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">the sky above us在我们上方的天空</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="注意-on-over-above三者的区别"><a href="#注意-on-over-above三者的区别" class="headerlink" title="注意:on over above三者的区别"></a>注意:on over above三者的区别</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">on一般表示物体与物体接触</span><br><span class="line">over可以描述动态而above不可以</span><br><span class="line">The cat jumped over the table(不能用above)</span><br><span class="line">兔子越过桌子</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="under-在…下方-与over相对"><a href="#under-在…下方-与over相对" class="headerlink" title="under    在…下方(与over相对)"></a>under    在…下方(与over相对)</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">under the desk在书桌下方</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="below-在…下方-与above相对"><a href="#below-在…下方-与above相对" class="headerlink" title="below    在…下方(与above相对)"></a>below    在…下方(与above相对)</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The fish dived below the surface of the water</span><br><span class="line">鱼潜入水下</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="near-在…附近-在…周边"><a href="#near-在…附近-在…周边" class="headerlink" title="near    在…附近;在…周边"></a>near    在…附近;在…周边</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">near the hospital在医院附近</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="by和beside-在…旁边-可互换"><a href="#by和beside-在…旁边-可互换" class="headerlink" title="by和beside    在…旁边(可互换)"></a>by和beside    在…旁边(可互换)</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">There is a hotel by/beside the river</span><br><span class="line">在河的旁边有个旅馆</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="next-to-靠近-紧挨着"><a href="#next-to-靠近-紧挨着" class="headerlink" title="next to 靠近,紧挨着"></a>next to 靠近,紧挨着</h3><p><code>强调紧接着的下一个相邻</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">the building next to school</span><br><span class="line">紧挨着学校的建筑</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="across-从表面-横过"><a href="#across-从表面-横过" class="headerlink" title="across    (从表面)横过"></a>across    (从表面)横过</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">go across the river</span><br><span class="line">穿过马路</span><br><span class="line">swim across the river</span><br><span class="line">游过河</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="through-从内部-穿过"><a href="#through-从内部-穿过" class="headerlink" title="through    (从内部)穿过"></a>through    (从内部)穿过</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">go through the tunnel </span><br><span class="line">穿过隧道</span><br><span class="line">walk through the forest</span><br><span class="line">闯过森林</span><br><span class="line">look through window</span><br><span class="line">透过窗子看</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="pass-经过-路过"><a href="#pass-经过-路过" class="headerlink" title="pass    经过,路过"></a>pass    经过,路过</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The old man walked pass the man without saying any words</span><br><span class="line">这个老人从男人身边经过，没有说一句话</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="in-front-of-在…前方"><a href="#in-front-of-在…前方" class="headerlink" title="in front of     在…前方"></a>in front of     在…前方</h3><h3 id="before-在…之前"><a href="#before-在…之前" class="headerlink" title="before    在…之前"></a>before    在…之前</h3><h3 id="behind-在…之后"><a href="#behind-在…之后" class="headerlink" title="behind    在…之后"></a>behind    在…之后</h3><h3 id="between-在…之间"><a href="#between-在…之间" class="headerlink" title="between    在…之间"></a>between    在…之间</h3><h3 id="among-在…之间"><a href="#among-在…之间" class="headerlink" title="among    在…之间"></a>among    在…之间</h3><h3 id="round和around-环绕-围绕"><a href="#round和around-环绕-围绕" class="headerlink" title="round和around    环绕,围绕"></a>round和around    环绕,围绕</h3><h3 id="along-沿着-顺着"><a href="#along-沿着-顺着" class="headerlink" title="along    沿着,顺着"></a>along    沿着,顺着</h3><h3 id="to-向-朝"><a href="#to-向-朝" class="headerlink" title="to    向,朝"></a>to    向,朝</h3><h3 id="toward和towards-朝着…的方向"><a href="#toward和towards-朝着…的方向" class="headerlink" title="toward和towards    朝着…的方向"></a>toward和towards    朝着…的方向</h3><h3 id="onto-到…的上面"><a href="#onto-到…的上面" class="headerlink" title="onto    到…的上面"></a>onto    到…的上面</h3><h3 id="into-到…里面"><a href="#into-到…里面" class="headerlink" title="into    到…里面"></a>into    到…里面</h3><h3 id="out-of-从里面出来"><a href="#out-of-从里面出来" class="headerlink" title="out of    从里面出来"></a>out of    从里面出来</h3><h3 id="opposite-在…对面"><a href="#opposite-在…对面" class="headerlink" title="opposite    在…对面"></a>opposite    在…对面</h3><h3 id="against-与…相反-依-靠"><a href="#against-与…相反-依-靠" class="headerlink" title="against    与…相反,依,靠"></a>against    与…相反,依,靠</h3><h3 id="up-沿…向下"><a href="#up-沿…向下" class="headerlink" title="up    沿…向下"></a>up    沿…向下</h3><h3 id="off-离…距离"><a href="#off-离…距离" class="headerlink" title="off    离…距离"></a>off    离…距离</h3><hr><h2 id="时间介词"><a href="#时间介词" class="headerlink" title="时间介词"></a><strong>时间介词</strong></h2><h3 id="in-在…里面-1"><a href="#in-在…里面-1" class="headerlink" title="in    在…里面"></a><strong>in    在…里面</strong></h3><p><code>在范围相对较大的时间</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">in winter在冬季</span><br><span class="line">in December在12月</span><br><span class="line">in 2022在2020年</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="on-在…上面-1"><a href="#on-在…上面-1" class="headerlink" title="on    在…上面"></a><strong>on    在…上面</strong></h3><p><code>表示具体的某一天，表示时间范围相对较小一些</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">on Monday在星期一</span><br><span class="line">on Christmas Day 在圣诞节</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="at-在某处-1"><a href="#at-在某处-1" class="headerlink" title="at    在某处"></a><strong>at    在某处</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">at 6 o&#x27;clock在6点</span><br><span class="line">at noon在中午</span><br><span class="line">at dawn在黎明时分</span><br><span class="line">at sunset在日落时分</span><br><span class="line">at the age of 10在10岁时</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="during-持续-在…期间"><a href="#during-持续-在…期间" class="headerlink" title="during    持续;在…期间"></a><strong>during    持续;在…期间</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">during past 2 days/weeks/years在过去的2个天/星期/年里</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="for-因…持续-因为"><a href="#for-因…持续-因为" class="headerlink" title="for    因…持续;因为"></a><strong>for    因…持续;因为</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">I have learned English for 2 years我持续学习英语2年时间</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="since-自从"><a href="#since-自从" class="headerlink" title="since    自从"></a><strong>since    自从</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">since last week自从上周以来</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="before-在…之前-1"><a href="#before-在…之前-1" class="headerlink" title="before    在…之前"></a><strong>before    在…之前</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">before Monday在星期一之前</span><br><span class="line">before 2022在2022年之前</span><br><span class="line">in the day before yesterday在前天</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="after-在…之后"><a href="#after-在…之后" class="headerlink" title="after    在…之后"></a><strong>after    在…之后</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">after 2 years两年之后</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="from…to…-从…到…"><a href="#from…to…-从…到…" class="headerlink" title="from…to…    从…到…"></a><strong>from…to…    从…到…</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from 6:00 to 12:00从6点到12点</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="by-不超过…边界-不迟于…之前"><a href="#by-不超过…边界-不迟于…之前" class="headerlink" title="by    不超过…边界;不迟于…之前"></a><strong>by    不超过…边界;不迟于…之前</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">by在表示时间点之前同before意思相近，但是before是范指时间点之前，而by相当于限定一条时间现</span><br><span class="line">by 2o&#x27;clock在2点之前</span><br><span class="line">by tomorrow在明天之前</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="until-直到…为止"><a href="#until-直到…为止" class="headerlink" title="until    直到…为止"></a><strong>until    直到…为止</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">until 12 o&#x27;clock直到12点为止</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="方式介词"><a href="#方式介词" class="headerlink" title="方式介词"></a><strong>方式介词</strong></h2><h3 id="in-…方式"><a href="#in-…方式" class="headerlink" title="in    …方式"></a><strong>in    …方式</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">in English用英语</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="through-通过…方式-穿过"><a href="#through-通过…方式-穿过" class="headerlink" title="through    通过…方式;穿过"></a><strong>through    通过…方式;穿过</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">We succeed through hard work 我们通过努力工作而成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="by-通过…"><a href="#by-通过…" class="headerlink" title="by    通过…"></a><strong>by    通过…</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">I go to school by bus我坐公交去上学</span><br><span class="line">I learn English by watching videos我通过看视频学英语</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="with-用…"><a href="#with-用…" class="headerlink" title="with    用…"></a><strong>with    用…</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">we write with pens我们用笔写字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="on-在…上面-2"><a href="#on-在…上面-2" class="headerlink" title="on    (在…上面)"></a><strong>on    (在…上面)</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">we talked on the phone我们通过电话进行交谈 引申用online线上来推出</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="原因介词"><a href="#原因介词" class="headerlink" title="原因介词"></a><strong>原因介词</strong></h2><h3 id="for-因为…-由于…"><a href="#for-因为…-由于…" class="headerlink" title="for    因为…;由于…"></a><strong>for    因为…;由于…</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This cat is famous for being able to speak这只猫因为会说话而出名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="with-…是和…分不开的原因-用于因果关系"><a href="#with-…是和…分不开的原因-用于因果关系" class="headerlink" title="with    …是和…分不开的原因    用于因果关系"></a><strong>with    …是和…分不开的原因</strong>    <code>用于因果关系</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The human is shaking with cold这个人冷的发抖(因为冷所以发抖shaking和cold是相关联的)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="because-of-接名词-because-从句-因为…"><a href="#because-of-接名词-because-从句-因为…" class="headerlink" title="because of    +接名词 ,because+从句    因为…"></a>because of    +接名词 ,because+从句    因为…</h3><p><code>(due to , owing to , on a account of)都表示因为...但都是固定搭配)</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The man didn&#x27;t go out because of/due to/ owing to/on a account of the rain</span><br><span class="line">因为下雨，这个人没出去</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="关于介词"><a href="#关于介词" class="headerlink" title="关于介词"></a><strong>关于介词</strong></h2><h3 id="about-关于-在…外面"><a href="#about-关于-在…外面" class="headerlink" title="about    关于;在…外面"></a><strong>about    关于;在…外面</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">think about想去关于...事情</span><br><span class="line">Could you tell me something about  your school ? 你能 给我讲一些关于你学校的事情吗？</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="of-此外的-附加的"><a href="#of-此外的-附加的" class="headerlink" title="of    此外的;附加的"></a><strong>of    此外的;附加的</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">think of想起...</span><br><span class="line">he thought of something important他想起了一些重要的事情</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="on-关于-可理解为在-事上"><a href="#on-关于-可理解为在-事上" class="headerlink" title="on 关于        可理解为在...事上"></a><strong>on 关于</strong>        <code>可理解为在...事上</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Would you like some advice on learning English你想要一些关于学习英语的建议吗?</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="数值介词"><a href="#数值介词" class="headerlink" title="数值介词"></a><strong>数值介词</strong></h2><h3 id="at-在某处-在某个点上"><a href="#at-在某处-在某个点上" class="headerlink" title="at    在某处     在某个点上"></a>at    在某处     <code>在某个点上</code></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">at height price在一个高的价值</span><br><span class="line">at a fast rate在一个很快的速率</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="by-后接度量的标准"><a href="#by-后接度量的标准" class="headerlink" title="by    (后接度量的标准)"></a>by    (后接度量的标准)</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">They get paid by the hour他们按小时那报酬</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="for-以…的价钱"><a href="#for-以…的价钱" class="headerlink" title="for    以…的价钱"></a>for    以…的价钱</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">I bought these books for 100 Yuan我用100元买了这些书</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="状态介词"><a href="#状态介词" class="headerlink" title="状态介词"></a><strong>状态介词</strong></h2><h3 id="in-在…状态中"><a href="#in-在…状态中" class="headerlink" title="in    在…状态中"></a><strong>in    在…状态中</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">in progress在进行(状态)中</span><br><span class="line">in a dilemma处于进退两难的境地</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="on-受到之下…支持-的状态"><a href="#on-受到之下…支持-的状态" class="headerlink" title="on    受到之下…支持(的状态)"></a><strong>on    受到之下…支持(的状态)</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">on a diet在节食(在节食支持的状态)</span><br><span class="line">on drugs吃药(在吃药支持的状态)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="at-在某个状态"><a href="#at-在某个状态" class="headerlink" title="at    在某个状态"></a><strong>at    在某个状态</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">at work在工作</span><br><span class="line">at dinner在吃晚饭</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="under-在-框架-前提-下"><a href="#under-在-框架-前提-下" class="headerlink" title="under    在(框架,前提)下"></a><strong>under    在(框架,前提)下</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">under construction在施工中</span><br><span class="line">under discussion在讨论中</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="排除介词"><a href="#排除介词" class="headerlink" title="排除介词"></a><strong>排除介词</strong></h2><h3 id="besides-除了…还"><a href="#besides-除了…还" class="headerlink" title="besides        除了…还"></a><strong>besides        除了…还</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">I like a lot of other fruits besides apples除了苹果我还喜欢很多水果</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="except-除了…"><a href="#except-除了…" class="headerlink" title="except     除了…"></a><strong>except     除了…</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Everyone went to the party except me每个人都去了聚合，除了我</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="except-for-除了…"><a href="#except-for-除了…" class="headerlink" title="except for    除了…"></a><strong>except for    除了…</strong></h3><p><code>用来对之前的内容进行反驳</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The part is great except for  the loud music这个聚会很棒，除了吵杂的音乐</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;一-介词的含义&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#一-介词的含义&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;(一) 介词的含义&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;(一) 介词的含义&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;​    英语前置词（preposition ，adposition的一种，还有后置词postposition），表示名词、代词等与句中其它词的关系，在句中不能单独作&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%A5%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E5%88%86/5695962&quot;&gt;句子成分&lt;/a&gt;。介词后面一般有名词、代词或相当于名词的其他&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%AF%8D%E7%B1%BB/5310343&quot;&gt;词类&lt;/a&gt;、短语或从句作它的&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AE%BE%E8%AF%AD/87544&quot;&gt;宾语&lt;/a&gt;，表示与其他成分的关系。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前置词和它的宾语构成介词&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%AF%8D%E7%BB%84/8481390&quot;&gt;词组&lt;/a&gt;，在句中作&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%8A%B6%E8%AF%AD/882&quot;&gt;状语&lt;/a&gt;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%A1%A8%E8%AF%AD/2017501&quot;&gt;表语&lt;/a&gt;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%A1%A5%E8%AF%AD/2647235&quot;&gt;补语&lt;/a&gt;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AE%9A%E8%AF%AD/2645898&quot;&gt;定语&lt;/a&gt;或介词宾语。同时介词的用法也很灵活，同一个介词可以表达多种意义，介词可以分为&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%8B%E8%AF%8D/6697743&quot;&gt;时间介词&lt;/a&gt;、地点介词、方式介词、原因介词、数量介词和其他介词。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前置词一般用于&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D/502047&quot;&gt;名词&lt;/a&gt;或者代词前面，表示该词与句中其他成分的关系。前置词后面的名词或代词称为前置词的宾语（如果是&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%B0%E4%BB%A3%E8%AF%8D/10189208&quot;&gt;人称代词&lt;/a&gt;，则要用宾格）。前置和宾语合在一起构成前置词短语。&lt;/p&gt;
